The key issue is: the Vite dev server serves requests for a Single Page Application (SPA). In a SPA:
1. The root `/` request is served `index.html`
2. ALL other paths should ALSO be served `index.html` (so the client-side router can handle them)
3. Vite has a fallback handler for this

